Package: pro.matthesketh.legacypodclaw
Name: LegacyPodClaw
Depends: firmware (>= 6.0), mobilesubstrate, preferenceloader
Version: 0.3.0
Architecture: iphoneos-arm
Description: LegacyPodClaw - AI Assistant for iOS 6 (formerly ClawPod). Native port of OpenClaw (openclaw.ai) for all jailbroken iOS 6 devices (iPod Touch 4, iPhone 3GS/4/4S, iPad 2/3/mini). Features: Siri-like overlay (home hold), Notification Center widget, lock screen status, app switcher widget, Spotlight integration, full gateway server, channels (Telegram/Discord/IRC/Slack), 10 AI providers, tool system, plugin SDK. Built with Theos. Inspired by PicoClaw (sipeed/picoclaw) and NanoClaw (qwibitai/nanoclaw).
Maintainer: Matt Hesketh
Author: Matt Hesketh
Section: Utilities
Tag: role::enduser
